# Populated workspace reference caches never enter this repo.
# Only the committed *.template.md files ship; /slack-sync writes the real
# workspace-users.md / workspace-channels.md next to them (or to
# $SLACK_REFERENCES_DIR), and those stay local.
references/*.md
!references/*.template.md
